quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  59,10,"Àwọn tó dé lẹ́yìn wọn ń sọ pé: “Olúwa wa, foríjin àwa àti àwọn ọmọ ìyá wa tó ṣíwájú wa nínú ìgbàgbọ́ òdodo. Má ṣe jẹ́ kí inúnibíni wà nínú ọkàn wa sí àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo. Olúwa wa, dájúdájú Ìwọ ni Aláàánú, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run.”<sup>1</sup>","[1] Àdúà kan nìyí tí a lè máa fi tọrọ àforíjìn ẹ̀ṣẹ̀ fún àwọn òkú mùsùlùmí."
  59,11,"Ṣé o ò rí àwọn tó ṣàgàbà ǹgebè nínú ẹ̀sìn tí wọ́n ń wí fún àwọn ọmọ ìyá wọn, àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ nínú àwọn onítírà, pé “Dájúdájú tí wọ́n bá le yín jáde (kúrò nínú ìlú), àwa náà gbọ́dọ̀ jáde pẹ̀lú yín ni. Àwa kò sì níí tẹ̀lé àṣẹ ẹnì kan lórí yín láéláé. Tí wọ́n bá sì gbé ogun dìde si yín, àwa gbọ́dọ̀ ṣe ìrànlọ́wọ́ fún yín ni.” Allāhu sì ń jẹ́rìí pé dájúdájú òpùrọ́ ni wọ́n.",""
  59,12,"Dájúdájú tí wọ́n bá lé wọn jáde, wọn kò níí jáde pẹ̀lú wọn.<sup>1</sup> Dájúdájú tí wọ́n bá sì gbógun tì wọ́n, wọn kò níí ṣe ìrànlọ́wọ́ fún wọn. Tí wọ́n bá sì wá ìrànlọ́wọ́ wọn, dájúdájú wọn yóò pẹ̀yìndà (láti fẹsẹ̀ fẹ́ẹ). Lẹ́yìn náà, wọn kò sì níí ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́.","[1] Ìyẹn ni pé, tí àwọn mùsùlùmí bá lé àwọn yẹhudi jáde kúrò nínú ìlú Mọdīnah, àwọn ṣọ̀bẹ-ṣèlu mùsùlùmí kò níí jáde pẹ̀lú àwọn yẹhudi. Wọ́n kàn ń tàn wọ́n lásán ni."
  59,13,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin ni ẹ̀rùjẹ̀jẹ̀ tó lágbára ju Allāhu lọ nínú igbá-àyà wọn. Ìyẹn nítorí pé, dájúdájú àwọn ni ìjọ tí kò gbọ́ àgbọ́yé.",""
  59,14,"Wọn kò lè parapọ̀ dojú ìjà kọ yín àfi (kí wọ́n) wà nínú odi ìlú tàbí (kí wọ́n wà) lẹ́yìn àwọn ògiri. Ogun ààrin ara wọn gan-an le. Ò ń lérò pé wọ́n wà ní ìrẹ́pọ̀ ni, ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀ sì ni ọkàn wọn wà. Ìyẹn nítorí pé, dájúdájú àwọn ni ìjọ tí kò ní làákàyè.",""
  59,15,"Àpẹ̀ẹrẹ wọn dà bí àwọn tó ṣíwájú wọn tí kò tí ì pẹ́ lọ títí. Wọ́n tọ́ aburú ọ̀rọ̀ ara wọn wò. Ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro sì wà fún wọn.",""
  59,16,"Àpẹ̀ẹrẹ wọn dà bí aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n nígbà tí ó bá wí fún ènìyàn pé: “Ṣàì gbàgbọ́.” Nígbà tí ó bá ṣàì gbàgbọ́ (tán), ó máa wí pé: “Dájúdájú èmi yọwọ́ yọsẹ̀ kúrò nínú ọ̀rọ̀ rẹ. Dájúdájú èmi ń páyà Allāhu, Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá.”",""
